Last Updated:
January 13, 2025
Arccos Golf LLC ("
Arccos Golf
", "we", "us" or "our") provides online and mobile services, including our mobile application (the "
App
"), website ("Arccosgolf.com" or the "
Site
"), and other mobile-communications and web-based services intended to enhance your use of the Arccos Golf products (the "
Products
"). We recognize the importance of your privacy and strive to be straightforward regarding our policies with respect to your personally-identifiable information.
This privacy policy ("
Privacy Policy
") describes the privacy practices for our devices, applications, software, websites, products, and services (collectively, the “
Services
”). You will learn about the data we collect, how we use it, the controls we give you over your information, and the measures we take to keep it safe.
This Privacy Policy supplements and forms a part of our Website Terms of Use ("
Terms of Use
"), available
here
, and our Mobile Messaging Terms (“
Mobile Terms
”), available
here
. Capitalized terms not defined in this Privacy Policy (if any) have the meanings set forth in the Terms of Use.
